Package: montyhall
Title: Monty Hall game in R using Roxygen for documentation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Clement", "Damoah", , "Damoah", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package simulates the Monty Hall game, where a player is asked to choose one of three doors. Behind one door is a prize, and behind the other two are goats.
